Privacy Policy
This privacy policy applies to the Face Swap AI: Deep Art & Magic app (hereby referred to as “Application”) for mobile devices that was created by Mustafa Alper Aydın (hereby referred to as “Service Provider”) as a Free service. This service is intended for use “AS IS.”

Information Collection and Use

The Application collects general information such as:
	•	Device’s Internet Protocol address (e.g. IP address)
	•	Pages visited within the Application
	•	Time spent on pages
	•	Device operating system

The Application does not collect precise location data or sensitive personal information.

Face Data Collection and Use

The Application uses face data only for real-time processing to enable its face-swapping functionality.
	•	Face data is processed locally on the user’s device.
	•	Face data is not uploaded, stored, or shared with the Service Provider or any third party.
	•	All face data is deleted immediately after the face-swapping process is completed.

Third-Party Access

The Application may use third-party tools for analytics or ad services, such as Adapty.
	•	These third-party services are bound by their own privacy policies.
	•	No face data is shared with these services.

Data Retention Policy

The Service Provider retains general usage data (e.g., app usage analytics) for as long as required to improve the Application’s performance. Face data is not retained by the Application or the Service Provider.

Children’s Privacy

The Application does not knowingly collect or use data from children under the age of 13. If you believe your child has shared personal data with us, please contact us at mustaalper@gmail.com.

Security

The Service Provider ensures that all collected data is securely processed using industry-standard practices.

Changes

This Privacy Policy may be updated periodically. Users will be notified of any significant changes through this page.

Your Consent

By using the Application, you consent to the privacy practices described above.

Contact Us

If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: mustaalper@gmail.com
